{"tid":1546688,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《太子站惡臭氣味的傳說》","createTime":"2019-09-06T11:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T11:21:20.000Z","uid":25559,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"593349edf5ec50ace0585167c1112f5b91b7fd2a","tid":1546688,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"《太子站惡臭氣味的傳說》<br />\n<br />\n如果在數十年前,有乘搭過地鐵的人曾經在太子站乘車又或者在太子站轉車,一定會聞到一股莫名其妙的惡臭氣味!而這種氣味很難用詞語去形容!但就令人印象非常之深刻!相信到如今仍然有很多人會記得。最奇怪就是,這股莫名其妙的惡臭氣味,並沒有在一段時間後消失,而是持續的散發!令人有一種不安的感覺!而這種惡臭氣味在往後一段很長的時間裡依然散發著...<br />\n<br />\n不過,原來在這股惡臭氣味的背後卻流傳著恐怖的傳說。有傳太子站的原址原是一個亂葬崗,所以有很多屍體埋葬於此。而這股惡臭的氣味就是由腐屍所發出來的。雖然原址被建成太子地鐵站,但由於屍體被埋葬於此時間久了,所以腐屍散發出來的惡臭氣味依然殘留著...由於太子地鐵站是建在地底的緣故,所以就充斥著這股惡臭的氣味了!<br />\n<br />\n聽日去太子站拜下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb1a16e77ef213256959fc180014225812a85cc","tid":1546688,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrwV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=16e39050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"864ed6b530b412cf6ad5f56c3059a65170db3594","tid":1546688,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9